id: pm-sdbo
title: Add remediation registry entry for validate_metadata_duplicate_issue_codes warning
description: "pm validate emits validate_metadata_duplicate_issue_codes:N (GH-235) as an advisory metadata warning, but the shared remediation registry (src/core/diagnostics/remediation.ts) has no entry for it. So pm validate --fix-hints surfaces every other metadata finding's fix command but leaves duplicate-issue-code findings with no machine-executable remediation, forcing agents to hardcode the rename/merge fix."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[3]: agent-ux,"area:observability","area:validate"
