updated_at: "2026-06-19T20:57:52.778Z"
author: claude-code-agent
acceptance_criteria: Add validate_metadata_duplicate_issue_codes to REMEDIATION_REGISTRY with an executable command + summary covering the rename-or-close-as-duplicate fix; the mutual-exclusivity test still passes; pm validate --fix-hints on a tracker with duplicate issue codes lists the fix command.
parent: pm-5oj5
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: "src/core/diagnostics/remediation.ts: new validate-metadata registry entry before the resolution section. Tests: validate-command.spec attachValidateFixHints assertion + remediation-registry.spec resolveRemediation assertion. Verified in sandbox (two BUG-7 issues -> fix_hints includes the title command)."
